      "span_text": "As reported in our previous work ( [CITATION_1] ), this classifier significantly outperformed the baseline single KS classifiers: by 11.9-30.7% (over DB + T W) and 13.4-31.4% (over FB + T W) (t-test with α < 0.05)."
